"function rho_v_many(pxs, pys, pws, phs, bx1s, by1s, bx2s, by2s)
    x1 = max.(pxs .- pws / 2, bx1s)
    y1 = max.(pys .- phs / 2, by1s)
    x2 = min.(pxs .+ pws / 2, bx2s)
    y2 = min.(pys .+ phs / 2, by2s)
    # max.(x2 - x1, 0) .* max.(y2 - y1, 0)
    sum(max.(x2 - x1, 0) .* max.(y2 - y1, 0), dims=3)
end"
